<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995860>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 17. Ambrysus brunneus. (14) Abdominal terga VI and VII of male showing accessory genitalic process of VI, (15) abdominal tergum VIII of male with pseudoparameres, (16) male genital capsule, (17) male genital capsule with terga IX and X (proctiger) removed." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995860/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

